note right of channels
  **Fan-out Pattern:**
  When a citizen's data changes (BG mutation),
  CGS broadcasts the StUF-BG kennisgeving
  to ALL registered systems.
  
  Each system gets the message through
  its own dedicated channel with:
  • Its own adapter endpoint
  • Its own endpoint configuration
  • Optionally its own transformation
  
  **This is why 29 channels exist
  for a single service!**
end note

